---
title: Extra Cheesy Cauliflower Galette with Filo Pastry & Apple Salad
description: We spy with our hungry eye a golden crunchy veggie delight. Roasted cauliflower and onion are tossed in a mustardy sauce and baked in layers of flaky filo with a layer of golden, melty Cheddar on top. Beware, everyone will be demanding more!

